    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels under MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1 requirements. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) was satisfied across all 5 evaluated operating points. The overall credibility assessment supports acceptance of the computational evidence for regulatory submission.",
